  "texts": [
    "The CNN-LSTM architecture represents a powerful fusion of the spatial and temporal learning capabilities.",
    "It leverages the strengths of convolutional layers to extract spatial patterns and the ability of LSTM units to model temporal dependencies.",
    "Through intricate design choices and variations, the CNN-LSTM model can be adapted to diverse domains, ranging from video processing to natural language understanding.",
    "Challenges include computational demands and sensitivity to hyperparameters, which require careful consideration and application-specific tuning.",
    "Gated Recurrent Units (GRUs) represent a significant architectural advance in the realm of Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs), which are the cornerstone of sequence modelling tasks in machine learning."
